{"id": "1475185902950285466", "channel_id": "1459507965366112370", "type": 0, "author_id": "763468659863584799", "author_name": "sugoitsubasanohaetaop", "author_bot": false, "content": "何を言ってるのか分からない！笑", "timestamp": "2026-02-22T17:42:06.892000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1459507965366112370", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "今日の〜シリーズver1.0", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1474930994149589155", "channel_id": "1474930994149589155", "type": 0, "author_id": "735553627539898400", "author_name": "kara4691", "author_bot": false, "content": "現在の配布札とイベント札だけは使用してます\n非表示札は自由枠です\n好きな札付けましょう\n　\n守秘者レベル　63\n警報級　Ⅴ　Ⅲ　Ⅲ　Ⅴ　Ⅴ\nスコア　380\n（Ⅴ　Ⅲ　Ⅴ　Ⅴ　Ⅱから変更\nそれに伴い3波〜5波変更\n下に追加してます）\n\n限定　サルバドル\n\n今期厳しいと思ったら比較的綺麗にまとまりました\nやってみて難しいと思ったら警報級下げましょう", "timestamp": "2026-02-22T00:49:11.898000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-22T09:08:32.119000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍵", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1474930994149589155", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【限定1キャラのみ】融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1474939135566418023", "channel_id": "1474930994149589155", "type": 0, "author_id": "735553627539898400", "author_name": "kara4691", "author_bot": false, "content": "1波Ⅴ級警報\n\n1番簡単です　全2戦\n1戦目勝てる火力があるなら密約はおまかせ\n札も適当\n\n1.シレスト覚醒→戦闘\n\n2.超次元空間にオレッタ0コスト3〜5枚収納、狂気解放を使わずに勝利\n\n3.ショップでオレッタ覚醒を買ってボス戦\n\n4.オレッタ覚醒+怒涛状態まで耐久、引けたらいっぱい攻撃して勝ち", "timestamp": "2026-02-22T01:21:32.963000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-22T05:54:33.222000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1474939135126012040", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-02-22-09-17-42-390_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 187937, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1474930994149589155/1474939135126012040/Screenshot_2026-02-22-09-17-42-390_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg?ex=6a33f0dc&is=6a329f5c&hm=14b24e9b474dc6902644f20c73ba87eb59998431e63a37ad622c4336374522e7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1474930994149589155", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【限定1キャラのみ】融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1474941741638619187", "channel_id": "1474930994149589155", "type": 0, "author_id": "735553627539898400", "author_name": "kara4691", "author_bot": false, "content": "2波Ⅲ級警報\n\nラモンナでヘロットの4コストを引っ張って撃つだけです\nヘロット覚醒して0コストで保持したり、4コストおかわりしたりしましょう\n\nアグリッパ2凸以上してるなら、0コスに刻印つけると便利です\n防御でも軟化でも好きなものをつけましょう", "timestamp": "2026-02-22T01:31:54.299000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-22T05:54:52.827000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1474941741374111845", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-02-22-09-17-45-608_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 207768, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1474930994149589155/1474941741374111845/Screenshot_2026-02-22-09-17-45-608_jp.co.altplus.boukyakuzenya.jpg?ex=6a33f34a&is=6a32a1ca&hm=f9a51365df1b231ef4799fe6b2473bf56b62c8b2ed4989161514ac53af9d292b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1474930994149589155", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【限定1キャラのみ】融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
